thread.title_full: Street Smart Transmission reviewed by Richard

author: Richard
title: Richard
text: Transmission arrived on time. Just installed so no opinion yet on performance. Very good service from Cory and others I talked to. Honored an earlier price Quote: even though price had increased. If the transmission is as good as their staff I will be very happy.
